# Propose Move-forward operator if front is not blocked
# If the tank is not blocked in the forward direction, propose the move 
# operator.

#%%%12 Sep 06
#To avoid infinite loops w/ other agent I've added
#a 10% chance of turning instead
sp {wander*propose*move
   (state <s> ^name wander
              ^io.input-link <il>)
   (<il> ^random >= 0.1
         ^blocked.forward no)
-->
   (<s> ^operator <o> + =)
   (<o> ^name move
        ^actions.move.direction forward)}
